promptTemplate:
[TASK] {{taskId}}
action: add-feature
branch: {{branch}}
files: {{files}}
description: {{description}}
{{#acceptanceCriteria}}
Acceptance criteria:
{{acceptanceCriteria}}
{{/acceptanceCriteria}}
---
Implement the feature described above.
Work on the specified branch. When done, commit and push the branch (NOT main).
Then use report_task_result with the branch name and commit hash.
